<p>
  This site is dedicated to providing an accessible experience that is
  perceivable, operable, understandable, and robost to all users.
</p>

<p>
  To do this, it aims to be conform to the
  <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG22/"
    >Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.2</a
  >
  at a AAA level. WCAG defines the miniumum requirements for designers and
  developers to improve accessibility for people with disabilities.
</p>

